title: Bills arrive in London
text:
Bills arrive in London 
Updated: Wednesday, October 21 2015, 06:30 PM EDT 
London, U. K. - The Bills arrived in London Monday morning and went to their hotel, which is 40 miles outside of the city. 
They're getting themselves ready for a week of practice, and their minds are on football. 
They don't start practice until Wednesday and the team has the day off on Tuesday, but after that, it's a regular game week. Bills arrive in London Entertainment News
